{"tid":2367160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(香港電台)民建聯：不少市民投訴收「天價」水費單","createTime":"2021-01-15T06:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T06:14:30.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cae168ecb5ef68ac70419a719f0290b5ee03dae4","tid":2367160,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>民建聯收到不少市民投訴今期的水費單數額驚人，形容是天價水費。</strong><br />\n<br />\n市民徐先生居於一人公屋單位，過往每期水費約17元，但最近一期要繳交1400多元，任職保安員的徐先生表示，月入萬多元，要在月底交過千元水費，感到十分吃力。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯表示，疫情下公務員在家工作，水務署職員抄不到錶，只是作出估錶，不少市民收到水費單都嚇一跳，情況不是只集中某一區。他們質疑水費的估算方式，又認為不能將公務員在家工作的「後遺症」轉架市民。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>民建聯促請水務署豁免5%的逾期繳費，在疫情的非常時期，與市民共度時艱。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570575-20210115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570575-20210115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=c1a88e05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570575-20210115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=60662512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570575-20210115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2c480270f3eca5bcaef74e6fb5e97b1d5ab2c626","tid":2367160,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"不如免水費<br />\n又叫人勤洗手，洗手唔使水呀？"},{"pid":"9f91c08e4b6654fae24d0dd55d4625b14985d602","tid":2367160,"uid":161935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"又想扮有政績<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}